<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SnapTalk | Connect, Share, and Discover</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        /* Optional: for smooth scrolling */
        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-white text-gray-800">

    <header class="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-lg border-b border-slate-200">
        <div class="container mx-auto flex justify-between items-center p-4">
            <a href="#" class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">SnapTalk</a>
            <nav class="hidden md:flex items-center space-x-8">
                <a href="#features" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-indigo-600 font-medium">Features</a>
                <a href="#" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-indigo-600 font-medium">Community</a>
                <a href="#" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-indigo-600 font-medium">Blog</a>
            </nav>
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                <a href="/login" class="px-5 py-2 text-gray-800 font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors">Log In</a>
                <a href="/registration" class="px-5 py-2 bg-gray-900 text-white font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors">Sign Up</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="container mx-auto px-6 py-24 md:py-32 text-center">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 leading-tight">
                    Connect, Share, and Discover What's New.
                </h1>
                <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    SnapTalk is your new home for sharing moments, joining vibrant communities, and staying in touch with what matters most.
                </p>
                <a href="/registration" class="mt-10 inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-indigo-600 text-white font-bold text-lg py-4 px-10 rounded-full hover:opacity-90 transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-200">
                    Get Started for Free
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-16 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
                <img src="images/uisample.png" alt="SnapTalk App Interface" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl">
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="features" class="py-24 bg-slate-50">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
                <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Everything you need to connect</h2>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">Our platform is designed to be intuitive, powerful, and fun. Explore the features that make SnapTalk special.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 mt-16">
                    <div class="text-center p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
                        <div class="mx-auto w-16 h-16 bg-indigo-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-indigo-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-bold">Share Your Story</h3>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Post photos, videos, and updates to a beautiful, chronological feed. Let your friends and followers see your world.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-center p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
                        <div class="mx-auto w-16 h-16 bg-indigo-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                             <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-indigo-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-bold">Find Your Community</h3>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Explore forums and groups based on your hobbies. From hiking to coding, there's a place for you to connect.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-center p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
                        <div class="mx-auto w-16 h-16 bg-indigo-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-indigo-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-bold">Real-time Messaging</h3>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Chat with friends and groups in real-time with our fast, secure, and fully-featured private messenger.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <section class="bg-white py-24">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Ready to Join the Conversation?</h2>
                <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-xl mx-auto">Create an account in seconds and start exploring a social network that puts you first.</p>
                <a href="/registration" class="mt-8 inline-block bg-gray-900 text-white font-bold text-lg py-4 px-10 rounded-full hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors">
                    Sign Up Now
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

</body>
</html>